WEBVTT

00:00.187 --> 00:01.673
Previously on "Greenleaf"...

00:01.700 --> 00:02.733
I have this old friend of mine

00:02.734 --> 00:04.535
is the head of bloomberg news now,

00:04.536 --> 00:07.271
and she keeps asking me whether
I'd be open to come up there.

00:07.272 --> 00:09.006
Good for you.

00:09.007 --> 00:10.474
What was your last church home?

00:10.475 --> 00:13.083
Greater Redeemer. I had breast cancer.

00:13.130 --> 00:15.164
That's why it's so nice
to be here at Calvary.

00:15.165 --> 00:17.833
I really feel supported.

00:17.834 --> 00:19.869
Bishop is definitely one of a kind.

00:19.870 --> 00:22.238
The only one that came
close was Pastor Skanks.

00:22.239 --> 00:24.040
Such a shameless hypocrite.

00:24.041 --> 00:25.908
- You don't know the half of it.
- Kerissa.

00:25.909 --> 00:27.743
Is that the church's
money you lost in there tonight?

00:27.744 --> 00:29.579
Give us Triumph II,
and you don't go to jail.

00:29.580 --> 00:31.781
You keep your church, and we get ours.

00:31.782 --> 00:34.016
Pastor Skanks just spoke
about the need for the church

00:34.017 --> 00:35.885
to take a firm stand against homophobia.

00:35.886 --> 00:37.787
I got a feeling you're
the one with the vision.

00:37.788 --> 00:39.789
Maybe.

00:39.790 --> 00:42.818
You know how many times
I've prayed not to go to jail?

00:43.660 --> 00:45.528
Hundreds.

00:50.434 --> 00:53.537
And to all those folks who want to say,

00:53.937 --> 00:56.272
"the Bible makes it very clear, Pastor,

00:56.273 --> 00:59.675
the Lord's position on this.
We don't need to discuss it."

00:59.676 --> 01:03.946
And I say, "well, let's find out
what else the Lord makes clear,"

01:03.947 --> 01:06.582
amen, because anybody
who wants to shut down

01:06.583 --> 01:09.986
a conversation with me by
slamming the Bible on the table

01:09.987 --> 01:12.888
without discussing what's in it
is going to have a problem...

01:12.889 --> 01:14.924
With me, at least.

01:14.925 --> 01:16.292
Let's see here.

01:16.293 --> 01:19.195
Hebrews 13 and 4 says,

01:19.196 --> 01:21.597
"marriage should be honored by all.

01:21.598 --> 01:24.433
And the marriage bed kept pure."

01:24.434 --> 01:26.602
Y'all know some of y'all
left your boyfriend's bed

01:26.603 --> 01:28.204
to get to church this morning.

01:29.873 --> 01:32.608
And have you heard
what he said about shellfish

01:32.609 --> 01:34.577
in Leviticus 11 and 9.

01:34.578 --> 01:36.879
- Right now.
- I know you have, and, yet,

01:36.880 --> 01:39.248
how many of y'all are heading
down to the shrimp boat

01:39.249 --> 01:42.351
after this to take advantage
of that allyoucaneat buffet?

01:43.587 --> 01:47.490
If we try to ban everyone
who does not follow

01:47.491 --> 01:51.127
every biblical law
from entering that church,

01:51.128 --> 01:53.529
none of us would be
sitting here right now.

01:56.300 --> 01:57.566
You got to understand,

01:57.567 --> 01:59.902
when God looks at each
and every one of you,

01:59.903 --> 02:03.272
he sees you through a prism
of the blood of Jesus.

02:03.273 --> 02:06.342
Without that blood, all our sins
would be laying before us,

02:06.343 --> 02:07.677
people of God.

02:07.678 --> 02:12.248
But through that blood,
we all can find the love of God,

02:12.249 --> 02:15.051
the acceptance of God,
and the oneness of God,

02:15.052 --> 02:19.422
a God who made us, a God who's
in us, and a God who's for us.

02:19.423 --> 02:23.259
Amen. So I say,
to the homosexual community,

02:23.260 --> 02:26.228
there is a place for you among us here

02:26.229 --> 02:28.664
for all of us that are
living under God's Grace.

02:28.665 --> 02:30.384
Amen.

02:31.201 --> 02:33.436
Okay. I see.

02:33.437 --> 02:37.807
It's not enough to say,
"who are we to condemn?

02:37.808 --> 02:39.175
Let God handle that."

02:39.176 --> 02:40.876
- Right.
- Let God handle it.

02:40.877 --> 02:42.345
It's not enough for us to say,

02:42.346 --> 02:45.081
like our brethren at Calvary fellowship,

02:45.082 --> 02:47.950
"all our welcome as long
as you hide who you really are

02:47.951 --> 02:49.752
and don't put nothing on social media."

02:49.753 --> 02:53.723
At a time when the laws of the
land that protect the rights

02:53.724 --> 02:58.161
of our gay brothers and sisters
are being rolled back every day,

02:58.829 --> 03:01.530
it's not enough to say, "God is love."

03:01.531 --> 03:03.499
It's time to get specific.

03:03.500 --> 03:06.836
It's time to say, "God loves gays."

03:06.837 --> 03:08.771
It's time to take a stand.

